<title>USA: Hyperion operating chief leaving.</title>
<headline>Hyperion operating chief leaving.</headline>
<dateline>STAMFORD, Conn. 1997-04-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hyperion Software Corp said Wednesday Peter F. DiGiammarino will be leaving his position as president and chief operating officer.</p>
<p>Jim Perakis, chairman and chief executive of Hyperion, will resume day-to-day management of the company effective immediately, the company said.</p>
<p>It said DiGiammarino joined the company last July. Perakis has been chief executive since 1985.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610.))</p>
